  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디저트 패키지, 박스 생산</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4f4d0bb-ea0d-41bd-8b31-f0fb3cd030fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9fb2ab57-7502-4d7c-9a79-69770fdecace\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e2c2310b-152c-460b-bf92-3c8646c13729\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5f374f3-cf45-4097-b92c-33682798b37f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-99b7eefd-82ee-4d00-96c3-77da73800edc\" style=\"\">제미나이로 그린 피자박스</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8bdc2a4-e6ec-41c1-85d6-a6339cb8e3f1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">디저트 박스의 대부분은 G형 박스입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">일단 디저트 박스는 여러 가지 형태로 만들 수 있습니다. 디저트의 종류와 내용물에 따라 패키지의 구성도 달라질 수 있습니다. 그리고 디저트 등 음식을 담는 패키지이기 때문에 유해 물질 포함 여부도 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7924bf22-9718-46cb-91ff-cdf96bb14ebd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a82ebdf0-fa1c-4aca-8e48-992e4bd91bf0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-10578fc4-950f-4b68-b4c4-3b13c34843f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e238d28-b75f-434e-9f61-1fe508a50e4d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f421878d-55e2-4032-ac5c-ebc5ae111c6a\" style=\"\">한솔 페이퍼</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96d0dc00-d454-4758-a615-8bf6410bdcca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:777px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28f22566-5664-4260-9164-b4f6af88fd82\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a694e5d6-e14e-4707-8e96-77fa9d45c803\" style=\"\">한솔 페이퍼 이미지 캡처</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1db71b1e-6a14-4163-b61a-535ea26f60dd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b451673e-f991-4447-a7a6-af86c8fbda03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d0b93bdf-ce36-40b2-ab79-ef3b7b2bab79\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>□ 형태의 장점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f2c10ca-b6b1-43ae-82f2-5b7079089a26\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bcb2e97d-4854-4b6c-a329-facd35980d8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a9cf55f0-6774-4627-bdb1-8efe46777768\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbcfc1ec-1771-4569-8e2f-338615aa4e8c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디저트 박스들이 G형으로 만드는 이유는 여러 가지가 있지만 몇 가지만 정리해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b79a55e-ca78-4d6c-8167-b2ce91c484f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34192e63-cafd-42cd-b5b1-932723178deb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbbd80d8-114c-48e6-a91f-1f0e367554b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-72885ae6-0a3b-48a2-89a7-77be97407dcc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 조립형이라 접착 풀이 없습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c7eabe2-1590-4d96-aa8d-441cb7ccbeab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f51e8739-21f1-4c56-b212-3f9af1df76f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26196d5e-f749-4090-a001-7971f7f4e748\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f80e7ba-619d-4d89-a91a-7cdac42a841a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">G형은 풀 접착 부분이 없어 디저트 박스 특성상 인체에 위해를 가할 일이 없습니다. 다만 조립을 하고 포장을 해서 직원의 손이 좀 발품 들어가는 것 빼고는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b52b841f-9782-4954-b50e-88954cdf183c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>가장 안정적인 포장 형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ef950324-f754-4f71-9af3-d108accdf95a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-edf14841-3313-46fc-8c3f-a6278ed19be8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5cb8c993-b681-4d1a-9d64-01e598baf984\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 조립이 상하분리형보다는 비교적 간단하여 끼워 넣고 쉽게 포장 형태로 만들 수 있습니다. 접착 공정이 없기 때문에 비용도 절감할 수 있고 조립 전 상태로 납품이 되기 때문에 공간도 싸바리나 다른 상자에 비해 적게 차지하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12f033a1-8f78-48ec-b364-0ddb2bab3d6f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-60493ef3-a61e-4458-950a-44997269c083\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f536ec40-4825-40a2-9809-734d7093bb1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fdd5a55e-3748-4f21-93f6-24f1a6c48c03\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 뚜껑과 일체형으로 만드는 형태 중 가장 쉽게 만들 수 있습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c9e2bb28-bb00-4ae3-a221-393050a72276\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ec2378fe-9ea5-4fa5-9fdb-b2a2b7c81a8b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-250663a2-b8a2-4cb7-bee8-ba8f09d31275\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c0dbf51-620b-4df7-b7a1-e624451f02b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품을 넣을 때 빠르고 안정적으로 포장하는 역할이 제일 중요한 부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7c6472d-88f1-48b6-89d3-07ba18bda2a5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-90a8a120-871c-4aad-8112-af4b3f416625\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 포장의 개념으로 본다면 가장 안정적으로 만들 수 있는 형태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eba2b484-e464-446b-8e27-9bae82790090\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2c73d28-080e-4a24-a9ec-3c19de9ecff0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ba7ad754-6254-4434-80b9-562ae7ff1558\" style=\"\">접착이 있는 B 형태 박스</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-97e15d87-f115-4bf1-8b52-552defd9635d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac935d4f-48cc-4d50-b939-bc39c85129d3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e5d1c28-0e86-4778-9965-2abd4f119c48\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 위 형태같이 만들면 접착면이 생기게 되어 있습니다. 한쪽이든 밑면이든 접착을 하면 공정과 비용이 추가됩니다. 하지만 조립할 필요가 없고 쉽게 패키지 박스를 만들고 제품을 넣을 수 있습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2fd12127-1b6a-493e-8166-2d109c9d2639\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>각각의 장단점이 존재</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-706fc6df-e1b2-4d34-b6c0-9eee8f5b4bd4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하므로 고객님의 제품과 환경에 맞는 형태로 제작하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0dd09ed-3947-4ab4-bda2-7ab4a105b5f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e62dbccd-dd1f-487c-a869-e503a37e6761\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcd45a82-2d3b-4821-8b2b-19378befcb17\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e6e8e20-182a-46ed-8f3b-64e6f18e0e60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ea2b00e-ca2b-4d7c-90ec-0d0c989ab008\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2d7f5383-91f8-40f0-8e46-c514e5d6571d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 공정과 사양을 자유롭게 바꿀 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddd6cd54-b33d-4877-9392-7fbdca816ca7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-33d86ddc-e96e-4359-a8ba-a88ee0854b7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57758e5d-cb02-4c73-bad3-02635a511b02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-62870460-3de1-4776-8d3f-73097b631714\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>G형은 피자 박스 형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31cc624b-4d72-43f3-9c89-5b504a6bbbe5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라고 보시면 됩니다. 피자 박스는 조립형이고 넓은 면까지 제품을 담을 수 있어 편리한 측면이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d67dfff-6d32-48e7-962e-267f4f15a3b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-382f8603-3bd9-4544-856b-8b4f73cfe217\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01ad3a81-940e-4291-bf1f-1dd13b2a2f36\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-35d2662d-607d-4abf-baf1-490b20679082\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거의 대부분의 피자 박스는 G형입니다. 합지를 하는 경우도 있고 골판지에 그냥 후렉소 인쇄를 할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23717560-90c5-4c92-aa24-90e59962f44b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50b7771f-b5ae-48be-9dca-fa8fcb44a6ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b116f024-0412-45b4-b95b-5dcfc2d7b613\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0a4fe63e-0090-4b37-82f2-440e0b747bcc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224006370823\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/224006370823</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3374aa45-bec1-4506-84e3-2ab2479e0452\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-739fa0b1-9c36-4c81-9118-4f89dcb32da5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f0826ce-f384-4385-be2b-7532e8004785\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형태를 변경해서 사양을 바꿔 자유롭게 제작이 가능한 형태라 가장 많이 사랑받는 패키지 박스라고 생각됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-40f95fed-1534-4db6-ab4f-907184e837a9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-414fbfc8-4d5a-46d8-bdd1-63694307fc78\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-54bd458a-742f-430c-b96d-13df1ecf2173\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">디저트 박스를 만들 때 고려 사항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-325b4a28-a1a9-40c3-8112-ea5d45b05312\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e1d8cc8a-fc9d-4fd8-85b7-f26c08f82a68\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a976e121-eb4a-4d13-87d5-9dee7c0c7842\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 친환경 종이와 잉크</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4fd4805f-eb30-4807-8299-0b7e77b41290\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8cd5024-4bc7-4086-8dbe-a7e00bc2b0af\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59a07268-5d1c-40fe-ad26-e6e603b5a610\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a18c19cd-230b-42c8-b1a2-4659e15f6ec1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가격을 고려하지 않고 친환경 패키지가 필요하면 여러 가지를 점검해야 하지만 그 중에 하나가 종이입니다. 요즘은 친환경 이슈로 인해 친환경 종이를 요구하는 회사가 늘어나고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7d5b6f45-5bb9-4c2f-9129-e4464afe44b4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87c17fd2-7b03-471c-85f7-5e6c0629a4fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c916fe1f-2dbd-47ef-ac72-3cac2d274407\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c53a3af-5a00-4d44-8f25-c76f61610c56\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이는 기본적으로 비닐이나 플라스틱에 비해 친환경이지만 그 외에도 여러 가지 인증을 더해서 더 완벽한 패키지 종이를 요구할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e99db2fd-8eb0-4b15-94e4-d763f86ebbef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76cb4391-440a-405d-bc8e-d7144ffd0ca5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4adc05df-c0a4-4376-b2d5-05b11e6cf303\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9eeec6a4-d57f-4ed8-a252-128ed6f2f8db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표적으로 친환경 종이들은 각 지업사의 인증 항목을 참고하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d132f242-cbf2-4f24-8b29-ccef5208c312\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97e23e60-d6a1-4b43-95b8-c95a755d3400\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0783bcd-c2c8-4e77-90f6-97ee17989814\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c51f1275-0111-4d16-a1e0-5fe793bc5f35\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>FSC 인증</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-477fab72-b838-4e11-a392-ecdb53590213\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36313abf-ab18-4553-ad0b-0274edac4d1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2e41a44-f93e-458d-9c15-a9a78c6dbb7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9166f5bc-efaf-40ca-bcd4-ed4e93c9aba6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86f68f3b-6cd4-41db-834d-caf5584ab918\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님께서 생각하시는 가장 대표적인 재생지는 크라프트지 계열입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77bd0a7e-e2d2-4d4a-b43c-0239cf61bb9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3f74797-8e92-4eb7-908f-7a1dabe4849d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-804627ce-d894-4e28-a90f-60c76f615843\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ca1c993-00eb-4042-8af3-6a50dc5fe4ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223890448493\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223890448493</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81f383b9-b84b-4f35-a5b0-06e9fa67f187\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88d7c121-1f6f-4bc7-9a60-2864c962f7b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d217d9c-89bd-439c-9e71-ef1272447d12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 친환경 잉크도 요구사항일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5bdecd2-5aed-48f1-afcd-018fbdd3fe13\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2ebe360-95e6-4ab6-b4a0-4460353e8357\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9eac488b-d852-4b47-8f54-db687f2f0d65\" style=\"\">동양잉크 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-23c4ba8a-f608-40e4-ae54-d8689b5d2a64\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f893e3f8-1a8a-48fc-aa85-8e86b92ea941\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b900b243-4f37-4e3c-b7ab-4320b9c60bc9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 거의 대규모 제작이나 대기업 쪽에서 요구되는 사항일 수 있지만 점점 더 소규모 제작에도 활용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2556f497-0cc4-4e76-8c87-f7c304382dea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-29f38750-b9af-4ac3-9628-70e5b53d4bf2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c55aa477-768a-41bb-b808-05a04a4c673a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c6f2424-066b-42c1-b1ae-342c4383c344\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 종이와 인쇄 외에 모든 궁금한 사항을 친절한 상담을 통해 궁금증을 풀어 드리고 있습니다. 고객님께서는 언제든 어느 시간이든 편하게 네이버 톡톡이나 전화문의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224045650495#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-07ce356b-8a88-4ff7-a568-d81be9331297\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53fad66e-d33e-4269-9c0d-7d2c4c83b8f0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2a6a08fb-993a-4f55-90e2-1d05b633328b\" style=\"\">디지트 박스 제작 사양 정리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd9ef046-cb2f-4f64-8b18-4a847cd80741\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-410993dc-a221-438e-9f43-ac7a1290a12d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1ef20aaa-c66f-47ff-b7f9-d95b256b373a\" sty