\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77e78cd0-93c9-415c-814d-9815f40fbc2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-146c5187-cc32-4bb0-81c3-21218f7339d6\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>합지 형태로 제작할 때</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-776940a7-a405-43bb-9197-4eed8eeb6a81\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c692190f-7fae-463b-9ca0-8959f1ab78e6\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5f2ab69-3e99-4fbd-8af5-1f8db2549132\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-670a2b24-0325-4893-b6f5-1c6b1a279f52\" style=\"color:#555555;\">SC 마닐라 계열</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8136c185-3875-4d5b-93b1-26e0c0849fd8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-953238c3-de17-4ba6-b54d-c47753887cee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또는 각종 특수지 외</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-442711bb-e761-454a-a78e-0d7f3ec52b9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8e373f5-1e7c-4f14-aa3c-6740e72271bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1ddcb27-68dd-4db3-9abe-c76422dbeedc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cfb16ac5-81f3-46a4-bbe6-51512c3c41e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합지는 제약이 없다고 볼 수 있습니다. e골과 합지를 하기 때문에 200g의 종이들과 콜라보로 합지할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f757263a-4c41-4b80-99b7-824b5556bb59\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a0b81e77-be8c-467f-b8db-1da51bf504c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c6947ae-92a3-426c-afdb-d18db21abb45\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02eb79d7-07f9-4e5f-82c2-37d8ce6ede7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">골판지는 백색과 황색으로 나눌 수 있지만 통상의 경우 백색 골판지와 합지를 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e786bb1-8ec2-4455-8c2e-347e979d5259\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045650495/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d936147-56d2-4f14-a2e5-130e719fa6b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-02bb279c-de16-485c-8783-0427efe4683b\" style=\"\">두성종이 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65c092db-e670-46c6-88fb-ac6b761bfbe0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d074e16-8ce0-41d3-9d2d-5e344fa4035e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cede7ce1-d0aa-4068-8b69-2e094a8eb29a\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>친환경 종이 사용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d5abac7f-37e6-4f26-b625-58d2cf7156b3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3dbdb2ba-6695-45e7-bbf6-68ae21531345\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ab5e5a7-3b96-4e30-978b-30461df9bcbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b0c66d1-0249-412f-8054-4e4752a9d3d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">친환경 종이는 별도로 문의하여 조건을 따져 봐야 합니다. 어떤 요구사항인지 또는 어떤 조건이나 문서가 필요한지는 확인하고 진행하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f43ab47-4f04-4216-a731-e81cba742e4f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca25993-921c-471a-bc90-2ec3289b1e21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ab45835-194a-457a-a254-6d2d9583fecf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77da8936-0176-4f3b-a377-53e92b21b2f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-740a425f-b2fe-4a3d-b1a6-5940ddd7b17a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-84a65b81-9c01-4bd8-933d-196fcf5f8845\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>□ 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b968f824-2ae3-4684-ad93-7b5ed415f0fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6fe811dd-5754-42b2-9d53-3bff3df10708\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-80b4d87b-8170-47a6-bbf2-05a7d70a510a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b94faec3-0404-493f-b1d1-1d72993351af\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>CMYK 일반 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa4e4dc9-55a4-45eb-b8de-401b5ffd2e05\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-502e43f9-1f5d-4340-b890-692313948367\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6643e72-e469-4e8e-ba62-11df532b9c79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-168ed826-13e5-4bc0-8e61-fcd00d591d4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">골판지에 직업 인쇄하지 않는 경우라면 일반적으로 컬러 인쇄하는 것이 보통입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e37aaf3-9ef4-4513-803f-925bd0258fd7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ddeb1095-2acf-4743-9896-859510ee7372\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40944f80-28b4-4241-b09b-56fe4a872cf9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-73986368-0eb1-43b0-a489-b21fe8b5412f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 일반 오프셋 인쇄가 아닌 별색이나 단색으로 제작하는 것도 많아서 이런 경우는 특별한 제작 업체와 공정이 따로 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33a21b02-e3b9-4cc0-bd2a-cb52592f0104\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f222754-4cf1-4346-9552-0ffef5f66fa8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5318c409-109e-49e0-b28c-964940f52b50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bbcb411f-566d-4839-8d54-ee928a8afe54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특히 골판지에 직접 인쇄하는 후렉소 인쇄업체는 별도의 제작 공정과 진행이 이루어지므로 반드시 단가와 납기 수량을 확인해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea768e4f-21ac-4d19-bc2a-a4d444c03a5d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e82bc517-0e07-4072-9a66-ee01716998ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b996e048-1052-4e00-9ac6-05722a257870\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9cfb448-3b3b-48bd-9e02-539ed3c06c1b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c731eb46-6f29-45e4-a5ab-f26e05b79128\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2b364500-f8ec-4e75-b0b3-807582d452c1\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>□ 수량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22494534-163d-4179-8d4b-203a0d6983e3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-53c44a24-a714-43a8-b1f6-8010b01248d4\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0f0da1b-13a2-4ecc-9eb2-79ccdb40b66d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1bfd741a-9bfc-4357-bef5-6be4b56ffa70\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>소량은 어렵습니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f931883-ff83-4667-891e-4007bafa12e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f6ab151b-d3c8-484d-b0a8-147a674cb810\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a91283c9-5fa7-4902-a231-d13732b109b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06cc0a2c-2f72-4bf2-858d-92ef8d76e9d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">G형 박스는 크기가 작은 사이즈가 거의 드뭅니다. 그렇기 때문에 소량으로 디지털 인쇄가 어렵습니다. 거의 대부분 대량으로 제작을 하게 돼 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d7151997-fd4e-4b5b-bfbe-b50134ff9444\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db5dd65d-d5f4-41e4-b4ce-ba1443b86002\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0edde9b6-ec15-43be-8de1-a2e02aa3496e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f0e1601-dff9-459f-a413-5fac851755ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특히 합지의 경우 소량 샘플이나 100개 미만 제작의 경우 @개당 단가적으로 무척 손해가 발생합니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe091a0c-5788-4caa-a222-956bc710977e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f61f144-a685-4b04-a80e-8e5ba8f5fdea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-defa